prodNameC: 岱安韶韻三碘甲狀腺素125I放射免疫分析試劑組
prodNameE: DiaSorin Clinical Assays GammaCoat T3 125I RIA Kit
ingredientsDesc:
1. [125I] Triiodothyronine Tracer Cat. No. CA-2684 1/5 per/kit: each vial contains approximately 7 μCi of tracer (<1 μg/ml T3) in 6 ml of phosphate buffered saline and ANS (8-anilino-1-napthalene sulfonic acid) with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.
2. Rabbit Anti-Triiodothyronine Serum Coated Tubes Cat. No. CA-2175 100/500 per kit 12 x 75 mm tubes are coated with rabbit anti-Triiodothyronine serum (titer <1 μg/tube) and packaged in a plastic bag.
3. T3 RIA Assay Buffer Cat. No. CA-2781 1/5 per/kit: each bottle contains 120 ml of phosphate buffered saline with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.
4. T3 RIA Control Sera, Level I & II  Cat. No. CA-2444, CA-2445 2/2 per/kit: each vial contains 1.5 ml of L-3, 3’, 5-triiodothyronine in processed human serum with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.
5. T3 RIA Serum Blank Cat. No. CA-2920 1/1 per/kit: each vial contains 1.5 ml of processed human serum with 0.1% sodium azide as a preservative.
6. T3 RIA Serum Standards Cat. No. CA-2921, CA-2925 5/5 per/kit: e
